    General Spindle model class. Implements the physical model Spindels. Inputlist: 1: State : [-] : On/Off 2: RotSpeed : [rpm] : Actual rotational speed 3: Torque : [Nm] : Actual torque Outputlist: 1: PTotal : [W] : Calculated total energy demand 2: PLoss : [W] : Calculated power loss 3: PUse : [W] : Calculated mechanical power 4: TemperatureOut : [K] : Coolant outlet temperature 5: CAirFlow : [l/min]: Compressed air flow rate Config parameters: TODO
